WEBVTT

01:55.640 --> 01:59.080
Do you believe it, Zuliang?

02:14.600 --> 02:15.560
Madam.

02:18.880 --> 02:20.010
Today's newspaper.

02:20.480 --> 02:21.320
Thank you.

02:21.720 --> 02:23.520
Are the master's books all packed up?

02:23.520 --> 02:25.480
The master's books filled several boxes.

02:25.480 --> 02:26.940
And the car has been hired.

02:28.160 --> 02:30.360
I can't take these boxes with me either.

02:30.440 --> 02:32.240
Please help move them to the countryside.

02:32.240 --> 02:33.280
Yes, Madam.

03:39.960 --> 03:40.680
Wanfu.

03:41.120 --> 03:41.600
Wanfu.

03:41.600 --> 03:42.240
Madam.

03:42.440 --> 03:42.920
Look.

03:43.240 --> 03:43.840
What is it?

03:44.000 --> 03:45.400
Your brigade commander.

03:48.160 --> 03:49.820
Is it your brigade commander?

03:55.800 --> 03:57.160
Look at these shoulders.

03:57.160 --> 03:58.200
This silhouette,

03:58.520 --> 03:59.840
this is Yunkui.

04:02.000 --> 04:02.800
No, Madam,

04:03.320 --> 04:05.050
it's too blurry to see clearly.

04:05.600 --> 04:07.930
Then go into the light and take a good look.

04:08.400 --> 04:09.360
Is it him?

04:10.040 --> 04:11.120
It must be him.

04:13.280 --> 04:15.040
I've always had a feeling.

04:15.560 --> 04:16.920
I feel that Yunkui is not dead.

04:16.920 --> 04:17.680
These past two days,

04:17.680 --> 04:18.560
a voice kept telling me

04:18.560 --> 04:19.820
Yunkui is still alive.

04:23.400 --> 04:23.960
No, Madam,

04:23.960 --> 04:25.400
this is too blurry.

04:25.400 --> 04:27.200
How could anyone recognize him?

04:33.159 --> 04:33.760
Come here.

04:33.760 --> 04:34.560
Madam.

04:36.120 --> 04:37.480
Twenty-one, twenty-two,

04:37.480 --> 04:39.120
twenty-three, twenty-four,

04:39.120 --> 04:39.680
twenty-five...

04:39.680 --> 04:40.200
Madam.

04:40.560 --> 04:41.400
Don't speak.

04:41.560 --> 04:42.920
Twenty-six, twenty-seven,

04:42.920 --> 04:44.240
twenty-eight, twenty-nine...

04:44.240 --> 04:44.920
Madam.

04:45.880 --> 04:46.400
Madam!

04:46.600 --> 04:47.880
I told you not to speak.

04:48.040 --> 04:49.520
Just help me count.

04:50.320 --> 04:51.400
Help you count what?

04:51.400 --> 04:52.240
Where was I?

04:52.440 --> 04:53.200
What do you mean?

04:53.200 --> 04:54.320
What number was I on?

04:54.320 --> 04:55.400
No, what are you talking about?

04:55.400 --> 04:57.460
You have to tell me what you're doing.

05:00.880 --> 05:01.880
Yunkui,

05:02.480 --> 05:04.610
he liked the broad beans I made for him.

05:05.000 --> 05:05.800
Every time he went out,

05:05.800 --> 05:07.200
I would pack a bag for him.

05:07.920 --> 05:10.280
He forgot to take them when he left that day.

05:10.280 --> 05:12.200
So I chased after him with the broad beans.

05:12.200 --> 05:13.880
I couldn't find him along the way.

05:13.880 --> 05:15.680
I thought I was going to lose him.

05:15.760 --> 05:16.600
Right there,

05:16.640 --> 05:18.200
I ran into him right there.

05:19.200 --> 05:20.280
If I walk from here

05:20.480 --> 05:21.560
back home,

05:22.000 --> 05:23.760
and the number of steps is even,

05:24.400 --> 05:25.760
he is still alive.

05:27.840 --> 05:28.520
No.

05:28.880 --> 05:29.880
No.

05:30.360 --> 05:31.440
No.

05:37.800 --> 05:40.120
One, two, three, four,

05:40.520 --> 05:43.240
five, six, seven, eight,

05:43.240 --> 05:45.560
nine, ten, eleven, twelve,

05:45.840 --> 05:48.200
thirteen, fourteen, fifteen, sixteen,

05:48.440 --> 05:51.240
seventeen, eighteen, nineteen, twenty.

05:52.480 --> 05:53.720
1,567.

05:54.520 --> 05:55.440
1,568.

05:56.040 --> 05:57.040
1,569.

05:57.680 --> 05:58.560
1,570.

05:59.080 --> 06:00.480
1,571.

06:00.560 --> 06:01.760
1,572.

06:02.040 --> 06:03.000
1,573.

06:03.240 --> 06:04.320
1,574.

06:04.560 --> 06:05.680
1,575.

06:06.000 --> 06:07.160
1,576.

06:07.160 --> 06:08.600
1,577.

06:08.600 --> 06:09.840
1,578.

06:09.840 --> 06:11.080
1,579.

06:12.120 --> 06:13.880
1,580.

06:14.440 --> 06:15.600
An even number.

06:21.320 --> 06:23.250
This is where Yunkui left that day,

06:23.720 --> 06:26.240
when he kowtowed to his father for the last time.

06:26.240 --> 06:27.370
It's an even number.

06:27.520 --> 06:28.640
He's still alive.

06:29.520 --> 06:30.880
Ma'am, what does this have to do with anything?

06:30.880 --> 06:32.280
This is too childish.

06:32.400 --> 06:34.930
My wishes with even numbers always come true.

06:35.280 --> 06:36.760
Do you know how many broad beans

06:36.760 --> 06:37.920
I packed for Yunkui?

06:38.520 --> 06:38.920
Ma'am.

06:39.040 --> 06:40.240
622.

06:40.920 --> 06:41.680
Do you know why

06:41.680 --> 06:42.800
it was 622?

06:43.520 --> 06:44.440
Because

06:45.040 --> 06:46.640
the day I met him

06:47.159 --> 06:48.680
was June 22nd.

06:50.200 --> 06:50.800
It...

06:51.120 --> 06:52.520
Does this have anything to do with

06:52.520 --> 06:54.360
our brigade commander still being alive?

06:54.360 --> 06:55.880
The day Yunkui died,

06:56.840 --> 06:58.159
did you see it clearly?

06:59.840 --> 07:00.880
I saw it clearly.

07:01.120 --> 07:02.520
What did you see clearly?

07:04.120 --> 07:05.960
I saw clearly that the position was gone.

07:05.960 --> 07:07.280
Was the position gone,

07:08.400 --> 07:09.960
or were the people gone?

07:10.400 --> 07:11.720
Ma'am.

07:12.640 --> 07:13.960
The position was gone,

07:14.600 --> 07:16.120
and the people were gone too.

07:16.120 --> 07:17.780
All 6,000 brothers were gone.

07:17.960 --> 07:19.760
I want to see him alive or dead.

07:19.920 --> 07:20.680
So,

07:21.240 --> 07:22.880
you didn't see him, right?

07:27.360 --> 07:28.160
Wanfu.

07:29.280 --> 07:31.210
You haven't been with him for long,

07:31.680 --> 07:33.440
so you didn't see clearly.

07:34.040 --> 07:35.280
I don't blame you.

07:36.960 --> 07:37.960
Father.

07:38.280 --> 07:38.560
Madam.

07:38.560 --> 07:39.120
Father.

07:39.480 --> 07:39.960
Madam.

07:40.080 --> 07:40.720
Father.

07:41.920 --> 07:42.480
Yujiao.

07:42.520 --> 07:42.840
Father.

07:42.840 --> 07:44.040
Everything is ready.

07:46.000 --> 07:47.400
Yunkui is still alive.

07:50.440 --> 07:52.040
Look at the photo.

07:57.800 --> 07:58.640
Right here.

07:58.760 --> 08:00.160
This is Yunkui.

08:01.440 --> 08:03.480
This is a photo of the Scouts visiting

08:03.480 --> 08:04.960
the Shanghai field hospital.

08:04.960 --> 08:06.440
Yunkui must have been injured

08:06.440 --> 08:07.680
and sent to the hospital,

08:07.680 --> 08:09.720
so he happened to be photographed.

08:10.080 --> 08:11.080
Wanfu also said

08:11.280 --> 08:13.160
he didn't see Yunkui die with his own eyes.

08:13.160 --> 08:13.880
No, Master.

08:14.080 --> 08:15.200
I didn't say that.

08:15.560 --> 08:16.520
You did.

08:16.680 --> 08:18.200
I said the brigade commander and the position

08:18.200 --> 08:19.040
are both gone.

08:19.800 --> 08:21.660
Dad, the hospital is in Shanghai.

08:22.200 --> 08:23.720
Let's go to Shanghai to find Yunkui.

08:23.720 --> 08:25.160
What? Go to Shanghai?

08:25.440 --> 08:26.280
I'm telling you, Master,

08:26.280 --> 08:27.640
you can't listen to Madam.

08:27.640 --> 08:29.040
Shanghai is a war zone now.

08:29.040 --> 08:30.240
The army could withdraw at any time.

08:30.240 --> 08:31.040
After they withdraw, it'll be

08:31.040 --> 08:31.920
the Japanese territory.

08:31.920 --> 08:32.840
How dangerous is that!

08:32.840 --> 08:33.400
Look,

08:33.559 --> 08:35.120
Madam is still pregnant.

08:35.200 --> 08:36.640
But Yunkui is in Shanghai.

08:36.640 --> 08:37.700
We have to find him.

08:37.720 --> 08:38.880
Madam, you just said it yourself.

08:38.880 --> 08:40.140
It's a field hospital.

08:40.240 --> 08:41.080
By the time you get to Shanghai,

08:41.080 --> 08:42.600
the hospital might not even be there.

08:42.600 --> 08:43.840
Even if the hospital is gone,

08:43.840 --> 08:45.840
the reporter who wrote this article is still there.

08:45.840 --> 08:46.800
As long as we find the newspaper office

08:46.800 --> 08:47.480
and the reporter,

08:47.480 --> 08:48.680
we can find Yunkui.

08:48.840 --> 08:49.640
No, Master.

08:49.760 --> 08:51.000
Madam is completely crazy now.

08:51.000 --> 08:52.360
Do you know what she just did?

08:52.360 --> 08:53.680
She took me to the bridge

08:53.680 --> 08:54.680
and paced back.

08:54.760 --> 08:56.280
She said if it's an even number, the brigade commander is alive.

08:56.280 --> 08:57.520
If it's an odd number, he's dead.

08:57.520 --> 08:58.640
Isn't this a joke?

08:58.640 --> 08:59.720
That has nothing to do with this.

08:59.720 --> 09:01.080
She insisted she walked

09:01.080 --> 09:02.080
1,580 steps.

09:02.600 --> 09:03.720
Then I said I walked

09:03.880 --> 09:04.880
1,581 steps.

09:05.160 --> 09:05.960
Shut up!

09:09.320 --> 09:10.640
You can't see clearly.

09:11.280 --> 09:12.720
I can see clearly.

09:19.880 --> 09:20.640
Yujiao,

09:21.560 --> 09:23.040
to be honest,

09:23.440 --> 09:24.600
my eyes are dim,

09:24.600 --> 09:26.800
I can't see clearly either.

09:28.080 --> 09:29.560
Is this Yunkui?

09:29.960 --> 09:31.320
Dad, look.

09:32.440 --> 09:33.400
'National Salvation Times.'

09:33.400 --> 09:34.660
This is today's paper.

09:34.880 --> 09:35.760
Front page.

09:36.080 --> 09:37.800
Time, location,

09:38.200 --> 09:39.360
and Yunkui's war zone.

09:39.360 --> 09:40.440
They all match.

09:40.720 --> 09:41.400
And

09:42.080 --> 09:43.960
I'm the only one who has seen Yunkui

09:43.960 --> 09:44.840
looking silly outside the window

09:44.840 --> 09:46.480
after waking up in the morning.

09:46.480 --> 09:48.360
I know I have no way to prove it.

09:48.600 --> 09:50.640
I don't know how to explain it either.

09:50.640 --> 09:52.640
But this is Yunkui.

09:53.200 --> 09:53.720
Dad,

09:55.080 --> 09:56.340
can you recognize him?

09:59.200 --> 10:00.320
Child,

10:01.040 --> 10:02.480
let me ask you,

10:03.120 --> 10:04.720
tell me the truth.

10:05.920 --> 10:08.880
Do you believe the one you saw

10:09.480 --> 10:10.920
is Yunkui?

10:14.760 --> 10:16.080
It must be him.

10:16.440 --> 10:17.160
Okay.

10:18.200 --> 10:19.560
I believe you.

10:20.880 --> 10:22.560
This is Yunkui.

10:23.960 --> 10:25.920
Yunkui is still alive.

10:28.800 --> 10:29.560
Dad,

10:29.840 --> 10:32.240
I want to go to Shanghai to find Yunkui.

10:32.800 --> 10:36.400
What Wanfu just said is right.

10:36.960 --> 10:38.440
Shanghai is not safe now.

10:38.640 --> 10:39.840
So you and Sister Liu

10:39.840 --> 10:41.240
should go to Wuhan.

10:42.120 --> 10:43.580
Aren't you going to Wuhan?

10:43.720 --> 10:44.760
Here's an extra ticket.

10:44.760 --> 10:45.680
Take it.

10:46.280 --> 10:48.440
No, I'm going with you.

10:48.840 --> 10:51.100
We can't be separated at a time like this.

10:51.120 --> 10:51.800
Dad!

10:51.920 --> 10:53.280
I promised Yunkui

10:53.440 --> 10:55.720
that we would never be separated.

10:57.840 --> 10:58.600
Wanfu.

10:58.960 --> 11:00.680
Ayi said he's quitting

11:01.000 --> 11:02.440
and going back to his hometown.

11:02.440 --> 11:04.280
Good, let him take these large items

11:04.280 --> 11:05.920
back for us.

11:07.640 --> 11:08.600
Wanfu.

11:09.120 --> 11:11.520
Where are the three tickets to Wuhan?

11:12.000 --> 11:13.280
Keep one for yourself.

11:13.680 --> 11:15.240
Sell the other two

11:15.560 --> 11:16.840
for travel expenses.

11:17.240 --> 11:19.080
Consider it a token of gratitude

11:19.760 --> 11:21.040
from the Zhang family.

11:21.880 --> 11:23.440
No, this... Master...

11:24.960 --> 11:25.840
Yujiao.

11:26.200 --> 11:27.000
I know

11:27.600 --> 11:28.920
if I don't let you go to Shanghai,

11:28.920 --> 11:30.960
you'll never have peace of mind.

11:31.320 --> 11:33.320
Come, let's pack and go to Shanghai.

11:33.760 --> 11:34.880
Let's go.

11:35.720 --> 11:37.640
Yunkui is still alive.

11:38.920 --> 11:40.960
Crazy. Everyone's crazy.

11:41.440 --> 11:43.440
This family acts on every whim.

12:03.400 --> 12:05.080
Whatever you plan to do next,

12:05.320 --> 12:07.120
you must heal your wounds first.

12:08.080 --> 12:09.080
Fortunately,

12:09.080 --> 12:10.680
no one knows who you are here.

12:10.840 --> 12:12.480
You are now No. 157,

12:12.480 --> 12:13.360
Officer Li.

12:14.240 --> 12:16.120
Our hospital has received orders

12:16.320 --> 12:18.000
to retreat along the Wufu Line

12:18.000 --> 12:19.160
to Nanjing

12:19.240 --> 12:20.480
and prepare to defend the national defense line.

12:20.480 --> 12:22.920
Tonight, all equipment and personnel

12:23.040 --> 12:23.920
will be transferred.

12:23.920 --> 12:25.840
When does the first batch retreat?

12:25.840 --> 12:28.240
The severely wounded leave first tonight.

12:29.240 --> 12:30.840
Liao Fengnian and Sun Huaiyi

12:31.160 --> 12:33.560
should have already retreated to Nanjing.

12:33.560 --> 12:34.160
Arrange for me to leave tonight

12:34.160 --> 12:36.360
with these severely wounded soldiers.

12:37.720 --> 12:39.440
You absolutely cannot appear in Nanjing.

12:39.440 --> 12:40.520
If someone recognizes you,

12:40.520 --> 12:42.380
you'll be arrested immediately.

12:45.120 --> 12:47.320
My 6,000 brothers died for the country.

12:47.520 --> 12:49.240
I can't let them bear the infamy of a deserter

12:49.240 --> 12:50.360
like me.

12:50.360 --> 12:51.920
They won't rest in peace.

13:00.040 --> 13:00.970
Brother Yunkui.

13:01.320 --> 13:03.080
You haven't fully recovered yet.

13:03.080 --> 13:06.360
Besides, the frontal battlefield is a mess right now.

13:06.640 --> 13:09.440
Shanghai and Taiyuan are both in imminent danger.

13:10.000 --> 13:12.160
Professor Shen, my university mentor, also mentioned

13:12.160 --> 13:14.090
that his friend Xie Yufeng's side,

13:14.160 --> 13:16.200
the Communist troops, have already gone deep behind enemy lines.

13:16.200 --> 13:19.240
This new force cannot be underestimated.

13:19.720 --> 13:20.650
Brother Yunkui.

13:20.720 --> 13:21.980
The world is changing.

13:22.120 --> 13:23.000
Future battles

13:23.160 --> 13:25.280
probably won't be fought the same way.

13:25.280 --> 13:27.210
Do you want to think about it again?

13:27.280 --> 13:28.480
I've made up my mind.

13:29.560 --> 13:31.220
Thank you for telling me this.

13:31.400 --> 13:32.920
I will pay attention to the new situation

13:32.920 --> 13:34.400
and act accordingly.

13:37.080 --> 13:37.960
Brother Yunkui.

13:37.960 --> 13:39.960
Are you still in touch with your family?

13:39.960 --> 13:40.720
Before going to war,

13:40.720 --> 13:42.080
I told my dad and Yujiao

13:42.400 --> 13:43.240
that if the war escalated,

13:43.240 --> 13:44.570
they should go to Wuhan.

13:45.080 --> 13:45.360
Right now,

13:45.360 --> 13:47.360
they should be on their way to Wuhan.

13:47.400 --> 13:48.860
Once they arrive in Wuhan,

13:49.080 --> 13:50.440
they will contact your parents.

13:50.440 --> 13:52.240
The postal routes are a mess right now.

13:52.240 --> 13:53.280
It's been a month

13:53.440 --> 13:55.700
since I last received a letter from home.

14:11.240 --> 14:12.320
Brother Yunkui,

14:12.760 --> 14:14.080
when we were operating on you,

14:14.080 --> 14:16.210
we found you holding this in your hand.

14:24.480 --> 14:26.340
Your sister-in-law gave it to me.

14:27.760 --> 14:29.690
Thank you for not throwing it away.

14:34.120 --> 14:35.760
What I'm most worried about now is

14:35.760 --> 14:37.890
the newspapers saying I'm a deserter.

14:38.040 --> 14:39.120
When my dad and Yujiao see

14:39.120 --> 14:40.040
this news,

14:41.760 --> 14:43.820
I don't know what they'll think of me.

14:44.080 --> 14:46.010
Or what kind of life they will face.

14:46.840 --> 14:47.600
Zuliang,

14:48.040 --> 14:49.320
Once the postal routes are restored,

14:49.320 --> 14:50.520
write a letter to your dad.

14:50.520 --> 14:51.880
Ask him to pass a message to my dad

14:51.880 --> 14:52.540
and Yujiao.

14:52.600 --> 14:53.440
Tell them

14:53.880 --> 14:55.080
I am not a deserter.

14:55.440 --> 14:57.720
Tell them I will go to Nanjing to appeal first.

14:57.720 --> 14:58.650
If all goes well,

14:58.680 --> 15:00.540
I'll go to Wuhan to find them soon.

15:59.760 --> 16:00.360
A truck!

16:00.360 --> 16:01.400
Stop the car!

16:01.480 --> 16:02.600
Stop!

16:02.840 --> 16:03.280
Stop!

16:06.160 --> 16:06.960
Hurry!

16:07.080 --> 16:08.410
Brother, give me a hand.

16:10.720 --> 16:11.800
Get on, quick.

16:11.840 --> 16:13.320
Brother, pull me up.

16:13.600 --> 16:14.160
Pull hard!

16:14.160 --> 16:14.960
Help me.

16:15.760 --> 16:16.840
Come on, brother.

16:16.840 --> 16:17.440
Give me a hand.

16:17.440 --> 16:18.200
Pull me up.

16:18.200 --> 16:19.260
Pull hard. Come on.

16:21.400 --> 16:22.240
Get on.

16:22.240 --> 16:23.360
Help me.

16:28.680 --> 16:30.600
Airplanes! Run!

16:33.480 --> 16:34.410
Take me with you!

16:34.880 --> 16:35.960
Wait for me!

16:46.360 --> 16:47.480
Don't go!

17:35.400 --> 17:36.240
Master.

17:36.680 --> 17:37.810
You're still awake.

17:38.440 --> 17:39.300
Let me help you.

17:40.080 --> 17:41.480
You can't help with this.

17:41.560 --> 17:42.120
You

17:42.560 --> 17:44.640
can't tell a Song edition

17:45.040 --> 17:46.520
from a Yuan edition.

17:47.560 --> 17:48.640
You'd just make a mess.

17:48.640 --> 17:49.920
That's true.

17:52.120 --> 17:52.880
Master.

17:53.440 --> 17:56.400
Are you only packing books in your luggage?

17:58.040 --> 18:00.040
I know you want to say I should pack money,

18:00.040 --> 18:01.640
gold, and jewelry.

18:02.200 --> 18:03.360
Right?

18:04.760 --> 18:05.840
These things

18:06.040 --> 18:08.720
are the culmination of my life's work.

18:08.840 --> 18:10.900
They are more important than my life.

18:11.680 --> 18:13.240
Then you should pack them.

18:13.600 --> 18:16.200
Pack them all. Don't leave a single one behind.

18:19.240 --> 18:20.000
Master.

18:23.720 --> 18:26.680
Did you forget something?

18:29.240 --> 18:30.370
What I promised you.

18:30.840 --> 18:31.920
The boat ticket.

18:32.760 --> 18:33.720
Boat ticket.

18:36.320 --> 18:37.000
Master.

18:38.360 --> 18:40.400
Then I'll take it, Master.

18:43.760 --> 18:44.820
Thank you, Master.

18:44.880 --> 18:45.940
Thank you, Master.

18:48.080 --> 18:50.410
Master, I can't help you pack these books.

18:50.560 --> 18:51.840
These are already packed, right?

18:51.840 --> 18:53.640
I'll help you pack your luggage.

18:54.320 --> 18:55.920
Where should I put this?

18:56.680 --> 18:59.360
That's for A'yi to take back to the countryside.

19:00.280 --> 19:01.200
Got it.

20:04.400 --> 20:05.120
Madam.

20:08.680 --> 20:09.520
This.

20:10.040 --> 20:11.770
It's chaos out there right now.

20:11.920 --> 20:14.040
The rich keep their gold, silver,

20:14.040 --> 20:15.440
and valuables with them.

20:15.520 --> 20:16.640
Boxes like this

20:16.640 --> 20:18.600
are the easiest targets for thieves.

20:18.600 --> 20:19.880
I think...

20:20.240 --> 20:21.480
Maybe we should put it in

20:21.480 --> 20:22.410
my old bag later.

20:22.720 --> 20:23.840
It might be safer.

20:24.960 --> 20:26.200
Sister Liu is right.

20:26.280 --> 20:27.920
Some people are really bad these days.

20:27.920 --> 20:30.120
They specifically target refugees with luggage to rob.

20:30.120 --> 20:31.780
What are you doing here again?

20:34.040 --> 20:34.720
Madam.

20:35.040 --> 20:36.120
I just came to see

20:36.120 --> 20:38.120
if there's anything I can help with.

20:38.560 --> 20:41.200
You've already helped our Zhang family enough.

20:41.200 --> 20:42.400
Thank you, Wanfu.

20:43.480 --> 20:45.200
It's my duty.

20:45.560 --> 20:46.440
Sister Liu.

20:47.000 --> 20:48.320
Wanfu is going to Wuhan.

20:48.320 --> 20:49.380
It's getting cold.

20:49.440 --> 20:51.500
Please prepare a padded coat for him.

20:55.680 --> 20:56.640
Okay.

20:57.600 --> 20:59.080
Thank you, Madam.

20:59.720 --> 21:01.360
Madam, are you...

21:01.400 --> 21:02.520
Am I what?

21:03.160 --> 21:03.760
Go, go.

21:04.560 --> 21:06.080
I'll go get the clothes for you.

21:06.080 --> 21:07.640
How can you come to a place like this so easily?

21:07.640 --> 21:08.240
Go, hurry.

21:08.320 --> 21:08.800
No.

21:08.840 --> 21:10.760
You, hurry up and go.

21:40.400 --> 21:41.840
Wait in Shanghai.

21:44.720 --> 21:46.280
We'll come find you.

23:52.600 --> 23:53.600
Excuse me. Thank you.

23:53.600 --> 23:55.360
Newspapers!

23:55.600 --> 23:56.120
Careful, it's hot.

23:56.120 --> 23:56.800
Okay.

23:58.000 --> 23:59.330
Let me through. Thanks.

24:00.000 --> 24:00.800
Excuse me.

24:01.160 --> 24:02.080
Excuse me.

24:03.320 --> 24:04.780
Stop pushing from behind.

24:04.840 --> 24:05.680
Master.

24:06.520 --> 24:07.280
Madam.

24:07.440 --> 24:09.320
I've checked in the large luggage.

24:09.320 --> 24:10.080
Here's the luggage ticket.

24:10.080 --> 24:11.080
Keep it, Mrs. Liu.

24:11.800 --> 24:12.360
Okay.

24:12.360 --> 24:13.040
Wanfu.

24:13.560 --> 24:14.920
Thank you for your hard work.

24:14.920 --> 24:15.780
It was nothing.

24:15.880 --> 24:16.940
I've asked around.

24:17.040 --> 24:18.280
The Meiyun to Wuhan,

24:18.400 --> 24:19.720
and the one you are taking to Shanghai,

24:19.720 --> 24:20.680
called the Ophelia,

24:20.680 --> 24:22.240
are both anchored in the middle of the river.

24:22.240 --> 24:24.120
We all have to take a small boat to get on.

24:24.120 --> 24:24.800
They said

24:24.800 --> 24:27.460
passengers for Shanghai will be boarding soon.

24:32.320 --> 24:34.800
Here we bid farewell,

24:35.200 --> 24:37.400
setting off on a long journey.

24:39.360 --> 24:40.280
Wanfu,

24:40.840 --> 24:42.770
please take good care of yourself.

24:43.320 --> 24:44.520
Take care.

24:47.520 --> 24:48.440
Please, Master.

24:48.440 --> 24:49.440
Madam.

24:50.280 --> 24:51.800
Master, Madam, take care of yourselves too.

24:51.800 --> 24:52.640
That's him!

24:52.640 --> 24:53.640
He's the one who tipped off the Japanese!

24:53.640 --> 24:54.240
Traitor!

24:54.960 --> 24:55.960
Beat him to death!

25:02.200 --> 25:03.460
Down with the traitor!

25:05.760 --> 25:06.520
Madam!

25:07.360 --> 25:08.620
Mrs. Liu, are you okay?

25:09.120 --> 25:09.760
I'm fine.

25:09.800 --> 25:10.530
Are you okay?

25:10.640 --> 25:11.280
I'm fine.

25:11.280 --> 25:11.680
Madam.

25:17.080 --> 25:17.740
Shameless.

25:18.000 --> 25:18.640
Traitor!

25:18.760 --> 25:21.520
Beat him to death!

25:22.000 --> 25:23.330
Madam, are you alright?

25:27.160 --> 25:27.960
Father.

25:28.400 --> 25:28.860
Master,

25:29.200 --> 25:30.200
what are you doing?

25:30.200 --> 25:31.200
Please calm down.

25:33.400 --> 25:36.200
Beat him to death!

25:36.400 --> 25:38.800
Beat him to death!

25:38.800 --> 25:40.080
Go to hell!

25:42.320 --> 25:51.400
China will win!

25:51.680 --> 25:56.520
China will win!

25:56.680 --> 26:00.560
China will win!

26:01.000 --> 26:07.880
China will win!

26:08.200 --> 26:14.040
China will win!

26:14.040 --> 26:15.440
Tickets!

26:15.640 --> 26:17.000
Tickets for Shanghai!

26:17.720 --> 26:19.360
Master, they are checking tickets for Shanghai.

26:19.360 --> 26:20.620
Tickets for Shanghai!

26:21.080 --> 26:21.520
Hurry.

26:22.000 --> 26:22.960
Let's go. Come on.

26:22.960 --> 26:23.760
Don't fall behind.

26:23.760 --> 26:24.600
Have your tickets ready,

26:24.600 --> 26:25.400
and line up.

26:25.960 --> 26:26.680
Don't push.

26:26.960 --> 26:27.520
Slow down.

26:27.520 --> 26:28.360
Don't push.

26:29.280 --> 26:29.940
Don't push.

26:30.000 --> 26:30.880
Don't push.

26:31.560 --> 26:32.220
Don't push.

26:33.400 --> 26:34.060
Don't push.

26:34.440 --> 26:35.720
Wanfu.

26:36.240 --> 26:36.680
Wanfu.

26:36.840 --> 26:38.640
This is our address in Shanghai.

26:39.080 --> 26:40.280
After you find Xiaoyue,

26:40.280 --> 26:40.880
write us a letter.

26:40.880 --> 26:41.680
Okay.

26:42.280 --> 26:43.120
Write to us.

26:43.560 --> 26:44.400
Write a letter.

26:44.400 --> 26:45.060
Write to us.

26:45.200 --> 26:46.130
Goodbye, Madam.

26:46.360 --> 26:47.760
Goodbye, Sir.

26:48.240 --> 26:49.570
Watch your own luggage.

26:53.200 --> 26:54.720
Don't push.

26:55.080 --> 26:56.160
Line up.

26:57.480 --> 26:58.040
Go one by one.

26:58.040 --> 26:58.960
One by one.

26:59.720 --> 27:00.520
Open the door.

27:11.000 --> 27:13.720
Who wants a ticket to Wuhan?

27:14.040 --> 27:15.080
I want it.

27:16.080 --> 27:16.880
Wait a moment.

27:17.000 --> 27:17.530
I want it.

27:17.560 --> 27:18.120
Don't snatch.

27:18.120 --> 27:18.520
I want it.

27:18.520 --> 27:19.850
Highest bidder gets it.

27:19.880 --> 27:21.210
Highest bidder gets it.

27:21.360 --> 27:22.720
Whoever pays the most gets it.

27:22.720 --> 27:23.640
I want it.

27:25.080 --> 27:26.160
Wait a minute.

27:26.440 --> 27:27.240
Wait a minute.

27:27.320 --> 27:28.160
Listen to me.

27:28.280 --> 27:29.410
If you want a ticket,

27:29.720 --> 27:31.880
elderly, women, children,

27:32.120 --> 27:33.720
and families have priority.

27:33.880 --> 27:34.740
Who has a child?

27:34.800 --> 27:35.600
I have a child.

27:37.080 --> 27:38.520
Don't push.

27:39.480 --> 27:40.080
Don't push.

27:40.080 --> 27:41.320
I have a child. Give it to me.

27:41.320 --> 27:42.360
Where is your child?

27:42.360 --> 27:42.760
Where?

27:43.080 --> 27:43.600
I have an elderly family member.

27:43.600 --> 27:44.640
Where is your elderly family member?

27:44.640 --> 27:45.440
Where is the elderly person?

27:45.440 --> 27:46.240
Right behind.

27:59.920 --> 28:00.640
I'll do it.

28:03.160 --> 28:04.000
Come.

28:05.200 --> 28:06.160
Be careful, sir.

28:11.000 --> 28:12.640
Come, sit down first.

28:13.800 --> 28:14.600
Where exactly is it?

28:14.600 --> 28:16.120
I'm so dizzy from walking around.

28:16.120 --> 28:17.160
Let's ask him.

28:17.160 --> 28:17.760
Sir.

28:21.000 --> 28:21.800
Give it to me.

28:24.880 --> 28:25.800
Yujiao.

28:26.640 --> 28:27.760
Are you okay?

28:30.240 --> 28:31.200
I just feel that

28:31.680 --> 28:33.810
we are leaving Nanjing just like this.

28:34.000 --> 28:34.880
My heart

28:37.320 --> 28:38.800
feels so miserable.

28:42.160 --> 28:43.200
Yujiao.

28:44.280 --> 28:45.400
Don't be sad.

28:47.040 --> 28:48.500
When the war settles down,

28:48.560 --> 28:50.160
we'll come back.

29:32.880 --> 29:34.480
When we board the boat later,

29:34.720 --> 29:37.640
don't forget your luggage.

29:37.760 --> 29:38.920
Alright.

30:06.560 --> 30:07.360
Boatman.

30:07.640 --> 30:09.360
After your boat reaches the Meiyun,

30:09.360 --> 30:10.200
when you return to the dock,

30:10.200 --> 30:12.440
can you detour to the boat going to Shanghai?

30:12.440 --> 30:13.440
Someone left their things with me.

30:13.440 --> 30:14.480
I need to return them,

30:14.480 --> 30:15.160
and then you can take me

30:15.160 --> 30:16.560
back to the Meiyun, okay?

30:17.440 --> 30:18.640
How is that possible?

30:19.320 --> 30:20.000
On the shore,

30:20.000 --> 30:21.520
I still have many passengers waiting.

30:21.520 --> 30:22.320
I'm very busy.

30:23.240 --> 30:24.360
I won't make you do it for nothing.

30:24.360 --> 30:25.240
I'll pay you.

30:33.600 --> 30:34.760
Alright, let's do that.

30:34.760 --> 30:35.920
Hurry up.

30:36.160 --> 30:38.000
Okay, everyone sit down.

30:54.360 --> 30:55.480
Mrs. Liu.

30:58.240 --> 30:59.840
Hand me that bundle.

31:00.480 --> 31:01.320
Okay.

31:02.760 --> 31:03.600
Not this one.

31:04.040 --> 31:04.840
The blue one.

31:10.920 --> 31:12.240
Where is it?

31:12.520 --> 31:13.680
It was just here.

31:15.960 --> 31:17.040
Wanfu has it.

31:17.600 --> 31:18.640
Where is the sword?

31:18.640 --> 31:19.920
In the bundle.

31:21.600 --> 31:22.720
Boatman, hurry up.

31:23.160 --> 31:23.960
If we're late,

31:24.160 --> 31:25.400
I'll miss the Meiyun.

31:25.680 --> 31:27.940
Don't worry, you'll definitely make it.

31:28.360 --> 31:28.840
I'm telling you,

31:28.840 --> 31:30.300
I won't pay you if I miss it.

31:30.440 --> 31:32.440
Okay, don't worry.

31:56.720 --> 31:57.560
Airplanes!

32:14.200 --> 32:15.200
Japanese planes!

32:15.560 --> 32:16.120
Oh no!

32:16.120 --> 32:17.120
Japanese planes!

32:17.600 --> 32:18.480
Japanese planes!

32:18.480 --> 32:19.880
Row faster!

32:21.360 --> 32:22.240
Master, don't fall.

32:22.240 --> 32:23.280
I'm fine, you...

32:23.400 --> 32:24.120
Master!

32:24.720 --> 32:25.360
I hope they don't bomb us.

32:25.360 --> 32:26.960
The boats over there seem to have been bombed.

32:26.960 --> 32:27.480
Master!

32:27.640 --> 32:28.240
Slow down.

32:28.240 --> 32:29.280
The Meiyun.

32:40.400 --> 32:41.720
Ma'am, be careful.

32:44.120 --> 32:44.760
Father,

32:45.160 --> 32:46.290
Wanfu is on the boat.

32:46.720 --> 32:47.120
Wanfu!

32:47.200 --> 32:47.960
Wanfu! Yes!

32:53.960 --> 32:55.920
Ma'am, there's a small boat over there.

32:55.920 --> 32:57.560
There's someone on it. Look,

32:58.760 --> 33:00.080
it's rowing this way.

33:01.160 --> 33:02.240
Is that Wanfu?

33:02.760 --> 33:03.720
Wanfu! Wanfu!

33:03.880 --> 33:04.920
It's Wanfu, Mrs. Liu.

33:04.920 --> 33:06.180
Father, that's Wanfu.

33:06.440 --> 33:07.440
It's Wanfu! Wanfu is on the boat!

33:07.440 --> 33:08.560
Wanfu!

33:57.960 --> 34:01.840
Good.

34:23.880 --> 34:24.810
I'm telling you.

34:24.920 --> 34:25.520
Today,

34:25.840 --> 34:26.840
anyone can leave,

34:26.920 --> 34:27.960
but not you.

34:28.239 --> 34:29.600
Today you are staying here,

34:29.600 --> 34:30.960
to watch us die,

34:30.960 --> 34:31.960
to watch me die.

34:40.800 --> 34:41.480
Congratulations to the newlyweds.

34:41.480 --> 34:43.480
Congratulations to the newlyweds.

34:47.719 --> 34:48.960
Zhang Yunkui.

34:49.520 --> 34:50.449
I'm telling you.

34:50.480 --> 34:51.810
Anyone can leave today,

34:52.120 --> 34:53.600
except you.

34:54.159 --> 34:54.960
Stay here

34:55.320 --> 34:57.560
and see how I cook.

34:58.000 --> 35:00.480
Okay, okay.

35:00.560 --> 35:00.960
Okay.

36:24.120 --> 36:25.000
Kong Erbao,

36:25.360 --> 36:26.960
where did you send the sword?

36:28.240 --> 36:29.480
I'm telling you.

36:30.200 --> 36:31.840
Anyone can leave except you.

36:32.520 --> 36:33.040
I want you to see

36:33.040 --> 36:35.280
exactly how we die.

37:21.280 --> 37:22.810
Kick him. Kick him to death.

37:24.520 --> 37:25.320
You're awake.

37:26.560 --> 37:27.080
Wanfu.

37:29.200 --> 37:30.000
You're awake.

37:38.800 --> 37:42.240
Wanfu, Wanfu.

37:47.360 --> 37:48.560
Where am I?

37:49.800 --> 37:51.640
Am I in the underworld?

37:53.120 --> 37:54.280
You are here too.

37:55.000 --> 37:55.480
You...

37:56.880 --> 37:57.840
Bite your tongue.

37:57.840 --> 37:59.120
You are alive.

37:59.640 --> 38:00.770
Don't you remember?

38:01.280 --> 38:03.840
Meiyun ship was bombed.

38:04.840 --> 38:06.920
Didn't you get on a small boat?

38:07.920 --> 38:09.780
We saw you fall into the water too.

38:10.560 --> 38:11.640
But fortunately,

38:11.640 --> 38:13.560
your boat was close to us.

38:13.800 --> 38:15.360
So the crew on board

38:15.360 --> 38:16.520
saved you.

38:18.280 --> 38:21.080
Yes, I got on the small boat.

38:21.760 --> 38:23.560
Yes, I got on the small boat

38:24.520 --> 38:26.600
just to deliver the sword to you.

38:28.800 --> 38:29.880
Where is the sword?

38:31.960 --> 38:32.890
Where is the bag?

38:33.280 --> 38:34.340
Where is the sword?

38:34.360 --> 38:35.240
Where is the sword?

38:35.240 --> 38:36.500
They are all kept safe.

38:36.640 --> 38:37.720
They're not lost.

38:37.960 --> 38:39.040
Don't worry.

38:43.880 --> 38:45.280
My... where is my wallet?

38:46.560 --> 38:47.680
Your clothes have been washed.

38:47.680 --> 38:49.040
Your things are kept over there.

38:49.040 --> 38:50.170
Nothing is missing.

38:54.880 --> 38:55.880
Come, lie down.

38:58.480 --> 38:59.880
Get him something to eat.

39:01.000 --> 39:02.000
Wanfu.

39:02.720 --> 39:04.640
We are really destined to meet.

39:05.480 --> 39:07.540
You see, you were entrusted by Yunkui

39:08.000 --> 39:10.560
to deliver the sword to Nanjing,

39:10.960 --> 39:12.280
and we met.

39:12.720 --> 39:14.980
This time, you delivered the sword again

39:15.000 --> 39:17.260
and escaped the disaster of Meiyun ship.

39:17.560 --> 39:18.360
This shows

39:18.360 --> 39:21.240
that God is blessing you in the dark.

39:21.680 --> 39:22.080
Right?

39:22.080 --> 39:23.120
Oh no.

39:23.960 --> 39:25.200
Oh no.

39:25.200 --> 39:26.000
What's wrong?

39:26.080 --> 39:27.760
Meiyun ship is gone.

39:27.960 --> 39:30.240
How can I go to Wuhan?

39:33.040 --> 39:34.240
Wanfu,

39:35.160 --> 39:37.960
you are on the Ophelia now.

39:38.240 --> 39:40.280
You will go to Shanghai with us.

39:41.240 --> 39:42.600
To Shanghai?

39:43.680 --> 39:45.880
The ferry ticket from Shanghai to Wuhan is more expensive.

39:45.880 --> 39:47.440
I can't afford it.

39:48.520 --> 39:49.440
What time is it now?

39:49.440 --> 39:50.920
And you are still thinking about the ferry ticket?

39:50.920 --> 39:52.040
Is life more important,

39:52.040 --> 39:52.960
or the ticket?

39:54.640 --> 39:55.600
Wanfu,

39:56.080 --> 39:57.940
you are a loyal and righteous man.

39:58.160 --> 40:00.560
Our Zhang family will never treat you unfairly.

40:00.560 --> 40:02.040
After we arrive in Shanghai

40:02.040 --> 40:03.440
and settle down,

40:03.720 --> 40:06.520
we will pay for your ferry ticket to Wuhan.

40:08.600 --> 40:09.360
Really?

40:12.720 --> 40:13.760
Master,

40:14.640 --> 40:15.960
you keep your word.

40:16.560 --> 40:17.640
With what you said,

40:18.400 --> 40:19.880
I feel much more at ease.

40:20.560 --> 40:22.120
Come, sit up.

40:22.960 --> 40:23.920
Come.

40:27.440 --> 40:28.040
Come.

40:29.160 --> 40:30.080
Drink some sugar water first.

40:30.080 --> 40:30.680
It's hot.

40:35.080 --> 40:36.480
Don't let him drink anymore.

40:36.480 --> 40:38.540
His stomach is already full of water.

40:39.800 --> 40:40.760
Honestly,

40:42.520 --> 40:43.400
Madam,

40:44.280 --> 40:45.440
I'm hungry.

40:47.160 --> 40:48.040
Mrs. Liu,

40:48.640 --> 40:50.040
get him something to eat.

41:07.640 --> 41:08.760
Another one threw up, look.

41:08.760 --> 41:09.400
Madam.

41:21.480 --> 41:24.480
Chivalrous and courageous.
